OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1775131865
OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledge income tax freeze
OL,4,Cand #4bn for new hospitals
OL,6,FWelsh Labour has pledged to freeze
OL,7,Frates of income tax, if the party
OL,8,Fleads the next Welsh Government after
OL,9,Fthe Senedd Election on 7 May.
OL,11,FSpeaking at her party's manifesto
OL,12,Flaunch, leader Eluned Morgan MS, said:
OL,13,F"I make a clear promise to the people
OL,14,Fof Wales: in the next Senedd term
OL,15,FWelsh Labour Government will not raise
OL,16,Fincome tax.
OL,18,F"Fairness starts with understanding
OL,19,Fthe pressure families face, but
OL,20,Ffairness also means action."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
