OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1775131865
OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledge income tax freeze
OL,4,Cand #4bn for new hospitals
OL,6,FCurrently the Welsh Government has the
OL,7,Fpower to vary income tax by ten
OL,8,Fpercentage points, but so far it has
OL,9,Fnot made use of its income tax powers
OL,10,Fto increase or reduce rates.
OL,12,FThe power to set these rates was
OL,13,Fdevolved in 2019 and were forecast to
OL,14,Fraise #3.6 billion in 2025-26.
OL,16,FOther manifesto commitment's include
OL,17,F#4 billion towards building new
OL,18,Fhospitals.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
