OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledge income tax freeze
OL,4,Cand #4bn for new hospitals
OL,6,FFigures published by NHS Wales Shared
OL,7,FServices Partnership show that for the
OL,8,Fyear 2024 - 2025 it would cost over
OL,9,F#1.04 billion to fix the backlog
OL,10,Fmaintenance costs across Wales' NHS
OL,11,Festate.
OL,13,FThe party have focussed on five
OL,14,Fpledges:
OL,16,FIn the latest ITV Wales poll, Eluned
OL,17,FMorgan is on course to lose her seat
OL,18,Fin the upcoming Senedd Election.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
