OL,6,FDespite a drop in vote share to 33%
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru is still on course to be
OL,8,Fthe largest party with a seat
OL,9,Fprojection suggesting it could win 43
OL,10,Fseats, leaving Rhun ap Iorwerth six
OL,11,Fshort of forming an overall majority
OL,12,Fin the Senedd.
